name: __ETextureSourceEncoding
doc: List of (advanced) texture source encodings, matching the list in ColorManagementDefines.h.

TSE_None: The source encoding is not overridden.
TSE_Linear: The source encoding is considered linear (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_sRGB: sRGB source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_ST2084: SMPTE ST 2084/PQ source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_Gamma22: Gamma 2.2 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_BT1886: BT1886/Gamma 2.4 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_Gamma26: Gamma 2.6 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_Cineon: Cineon source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_REDLog: RED Log source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_REDLog3G10: RED Log3G10 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_SLog1: Sony SLog1 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_SLog2: Sony SLog2 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_SLog3: Sony SLog3 source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_AlexaV3LogC: ARRI Alexa V3 LogC source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_CanonLog: Canon Log source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_ProTune: GoPro ProTune source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
TSE_VLog: Panasonic V-Log source encoding to be linearized (before optional sRGB encoding is applied).
